extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Pendulum Monsters appear in full force in Duelist Alliance! Half Monster Card and half Spell Card, these magical creatures can swing the tide of battle with Pendulum Summons, the powerful new game mechanic for the Yu-Gi-Oh! TCG. Duelist Alliance also introduces several tournament-level Deck themes that’ll delight Duelists with their intriguing strategies.
